[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1036","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1036.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1315","title":"DEC OpenVMS DECnet/OSI 权限提升与拒绝服务漏洞","description":"DECnet/OSI for OpenVMS 5.8 之前版本中存在安全漏洞，DEC Alpha AXP 和 VAX/VMS 系统上的本地用户可利用该漏洞提升权限或导致拒绝服务。该漏洞源于 DECnet 网络协议栈在处理特定协议数据时存在边界条件缺陷，攻击者通过向受影响系统发送特制的 DECnet 数据包，可触发协议栈处理异常，进而造成系统服务崩溃或获取非授权访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1315"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:10.717","remediation":"升级 DECnet/OSI for OpenVMS 至 5.8 或更高版本。如无法升级，在非必要系统上禁用 DECnet/OSI 协议栈，限制本地用户对敏感系统组件的访问权限，并监控系统审计日志中异常的权限提升行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/f-04.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1315.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1315","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1315.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1315.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8jgc-f2hf-74fp/GHSA-8jgc-f2hf-74fp.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84458/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1315.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1036.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1035","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1035.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1307","title":"Novell UnixWare urestore 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Novell UnixWare 1.1 的 urestore 工具存在权限许可漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该工具在处理恢复操作时未正确限制特权执行路径的缺陷，通过精心构造的恢复数据或参数触发权限提升，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Novell UnixWare 1.1 版本，需本地访问权限，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1307"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:09.703","remediation":"从 Novell 官方渠道获取并安装针对 UnixWare 1.1 urestore 漏洞的安全补丁（参见 CIAC Bulletin F-06）。如无法安装补丁，可执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/urestore` 移除该命令的 setuid 权限位，作为临时缓解措施。建议升级至受支持的 Unix 或 Linux 发行版，从根本上规避该产品已停止安全更新的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/f-06.shtml","http://www.dataguard.no/bugtraq/1994_4/0676.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1307.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1307","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1307.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1307.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cr84-5qj8-f776/GHSA-cr84-5qj8-f776.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1307.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fca28a80-1505-4ad5-962e-45d3a10f89e6.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1035.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1034","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1034.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1300","title":"Cray UNICOS 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Cray UNICOS 6.0 和 6.1 版本中的 accton 工具存在任意文件读取漏洞。本地攻击者利用该工具对系统记账配置文件的处理缺陷，可读取系统上任意文件内容，同时可修改系统记账配置，导致敏感信息泄露和系统审计功能异常。该漏洞需要本地用户权限才能利用，攻击复杂度较低，影响范围限于 Cray UNICOS 特定版本。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1300"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:08.807","remediation":"升级到 Cray UNICOS 6.2 及以上版本，该版本已修复 accton 命令的权限检查缺陷。如无法升级，可移除 accton 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/accton）以消除本地提权与任意文件读取风险，但会牺牲记账功能。作为替代方案，限制可登录系统的用户范围，仅授予可信用户 shell 访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/b-31.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1300.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1300","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1300.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1300.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9226-8p5v-w2mm/GHSA-9226-8p5v-w2mm.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1300.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001018.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d8fd4edc-ae2f-41cf-85a2-4016ce7faf61.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1034.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1032","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1032.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1290","title":"nftp FTP 客户端缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"nftp FTP 客户端 1.40 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过搭建恶意 FTP 服务器，向连接至此服务器的客户端发送超长响应字符串触发缓冲区溢出，导致客户端拒绝服务，在特定条件下可能实现任意代码执行。攻击者需要诱导目标用户主动连接至恶意 FTP 服务器进行利用，属于客户端侧漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1290"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:07.313","remediation":"升级至 nftp 1.41 或更高版本（1.41 版本已明确修复该安全漏洞），建议直接使用最终版本 1.71。nftp 项目已于 2002 年停止维护，建议迁移至仍在维护的 FTP 客户端（如 lftp、curl）作为长期方案。临时缓解措施：避免使用 nftp 连接不可信的 FTP 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91127951426494&w=2","http://www.ayukov.com/nftp/history.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1397","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1290.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1290","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1290.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1290.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g5wr-v48w-5f62/GHSA-g5wr-v48w-5f62.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87793/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1290.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1032.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1031","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1031.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1287","title":"Analog 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Analog 3.0 及更早版本存在任意文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 forms 接口提交特制请求，利用该漏洞读取服务器上的任意文件，包括配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息，导致信息泄露。该漏洞源于 forms 接口未对用户输入的文件路径参数进行充分校验和过滤，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用目录遍历技术读取任意文件。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1287"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:06.927","remediation":"升级 Analog 至 4.0 以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。如无法升级，可在 Web 服务器配置中限制对 Analog forms 接口的访问，或禁用 forms 功能，仅允许授信 IP 访问。同时避免将 Analog 的 CGI 接口放置在公网可访问目录下。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.statslab.cam.ac.uk/~sret1/analog/security.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1410","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1287","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1287.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f974-p775-h8x3/GHSA-f974-p775-h8x3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87844/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1287.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1031.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1030","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1030.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1279","title":"IBM AS/400 与 Microsoft SNA Server 共享文件夹信息泄露漏洞","description":"AS/400 共享文件夹功能与 Microsoft SNA Server 3.0 及更早版本交互时存在权限控制缺陷。当多个用户共享相同的本地 APPC LU（逻辑单元）时，SNA Server 未能正确隔离用户之间的文件夹访问权限，导致用户可越权查看其他用户的共享文件夹内容，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击者只需在共享同一 APPC LU 的环境中拥有合法用户身份即可利用，无需额外认证或复杂操作。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1279"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:05.937","remediation":"升级至 Microsoft SNA Server 4.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复共享 Local APPC LU 导致的文件夹泄露问题。如无法升级，可为每个用户配置独立的 Local APPC LU 别名，避免不同用户共享同一 LU，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q138/0/01.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1548","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1279","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1279.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3qcq-w2m6-vwwx/GHSA-3qcq-w2m6-vwwx.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87845/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1279.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001013.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1030.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1026","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1026.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1259","title":"Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh Edition 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Office 98 Macintosh 版在创建文件时未对分配的磁盘空间进行初始化清理，导致先前删除文件中的残留数据被写入新创建的 Office 文件中，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击者通过获取目标用户的 Office 文档，即可从中提取可能包含密码、私人通信等内容的残余数据。该漏洞影响 Office 98 Macintosh Edition，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，需本地文件访问权限方可利用。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1259"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.430","remediation":"建议升级至 Microsoft Office 2001 for Mac 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。作为临时缓解措施，在保存 Office 文件前使用磁盘擦除工具对文件存储区域进行清零处理，或使用文件加密软件保护敏感数据以防止信息泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q189/5/29.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1780","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1259","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1259.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4fg5-9xqq-h6cq/GHSA-4fg5-9xqq-h6cq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87853/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1259.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_infor.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1026.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1012","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1223","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 ASP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 的 ASP 功能处理 URL 时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送包含大量 \"/\" 字符的恶意 URL 请求至 ASP 页面，触发 IIS 服务进程消耗过多系统资源而导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0 版本，攻击复杂度低，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1223"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:58.883","remediation":"升级至 Microsoft IIS 4.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可通过 URLScan 工具限制请求路径长度，或配置 IIS 过滤器拦截包含超长路径的 ASP 请求以缓解 DoS 风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q187/5/03.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3892","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1223.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1223.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1223","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1223.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1223.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cj4j-jmwc-f6jm/GHSA-cj4j-jmwc-f6jm.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87550/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1223.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1012.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1012.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1012.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1011","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1222","title":"微软 Windows NT 4.0 Netbt.sys 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系统的 Netbt.sys 驱动（负责 NetBIOS over TCP/IP 名称解析）存在拒绝服务漏洞。当系统作为客户端向远程 DNS 服务器发起主机名查询时，若攻击者能够控制或伪造该 DNS 服务器（例如通过中间人攻击或劫持 DNS 响应），使其返回一个 IP 地址为 0.0.0.0 的异常解析结果，Netbt.sys 在处理该非法地址时会触发缺陷，导致系统崩溃并停止响应。该漏洞仅影响 Windows NT 4.0 操作系统，攻击条件为攻击者能够向目标主机返回恶意构造的 DNS 解析响应，利用方式是通过操纵 DNS 服务器返回 0.0.0.0 地址以引发远程拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1222"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:58.753","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本（如 Windows 2000/XP/Server 2003），并应用微软安全公告 MS99-037 发布的补丁（Q269874）。若无法立即升级，请在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信任的 DNS 服务器（如企业内部 DNS），禁止外部 DNS 解析请求，并在主机防火墙层面禁止 NetBIOS over TCP/IP（NetBT）协议端口（UDP/TCP 137、138、139、445）对外暴露，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q188/5/71.ASP","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3893","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1222.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1222","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1222.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f298f72e4ec0bc0f6b7151db8bb167727c83d2d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1222.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2wcg-78mh-f9m8/GHSA-2wcg-78mh-f9m8.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87559/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1222.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001008.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1010","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1010.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1206","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10819,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10841}}","description":"该漏洞存在于 SystemSoft SystemWizard 软件包中，该软件包在 HP Pavilion PC 以及可能的其他平台和操作系统（如 Windows 98）上安装时，会创建两个被标记为可安全脚本的 ActiveX 控件。攻击者可以通过引用这些控件（包括 Launch 控制和 RegObj 控制）来构造恶意网页，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。由于这些控件的安全标记 bypassed，攻击者无需任何身份验证即可远程触发此漏洞。漏洞影响范围广泛，不仅限于 HP Pavilion PC，可能涉及其他安装了 SystemWizard 的平台。此外，两个 ActiveX 控件（Launch 控制和 RegObj 控制）中的任意一个都能被利用，为攻击提供了两种途径。这一漏洞允许攻击者在目标计算机上执行任意代码，可能导致系统完整性受损、数据泄露或进一步的攻击扩散。目前尚未有针对此漏洞的官方补丁，但 Microsoft 建议禁用不信任的 ActiveX 控件或使用最新安全更新以减轻风险。攻击者可以通过在目标系统上加载恶意的网页或内容来触发此漏洞，只要用户访问了包含恶意引用的网页即可，而无需用户的任何交互或权限提升。攻击可以通过在浏览器中加载自定义网页来实现，当网页包含对这两个 ActiveX 控件的引用时，系统将自动尝试执行这些控件的安全脚本，从而允许攻击者注入和执行任意代码。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1206"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:56.753","remediation":"建议立即卸载 HP Pavilion 预装的 SystemSoft SystemWizard 包，或在 Internet Explorer 中将\"对未标记为可安全执行脚本的 ActiveX 控件初始化并执行脚本\"设置为\"禁用\"，并在\"受信任站点\"区域移除不受信任站点。如无法卸载，可在注册表中删除 Launch 和 RegObj 两个 ActiveX 控件的 CLSID 键值（HKCR\\\\CLSID\\\\{...}）以禁用其脚本调用。建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本以彻底消除该漏洞风险。作为临时缓解，可在防火墙层面阻断恶意网页访问或禁用 ActiveX 控件运行权限。建议参考 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 及 HP 安全公告获取补丁补丁包进行彻底修复。升级至 Windows 2000 SP4 或更高版本可彻底消除该漏洞风险。建议卸载 SystemWizard 组件或在注册表中删除相关 ActiveX 控件的 CLSID 键值（HKCR\\\\CLSID\\\\{...}）。作为临时缓解，可在 IE 安全设置中将\"对未标记为安全的 ActiveX 控件初始化并执行脚本\"设为\"禁用\"，并在受信任站点区域移除不可信站点。建议参考 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 应用补丁或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本彻底修复。作为临时缓解措施，可在防火墙层面阻断恶意网页访问或禁用 ActiveX 控件运行权限。建议卸载 SystemSoft SystemWizard 包或在注册表中删除 Launch 和 RegObj 两个 ActiveX 控件的 CLSID 键值以禁用其脚本调用能力。升级至 Windows 2000 SP4 或更高版本可彻底消除该漏洞风险。建议参考 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 及 HP 安全公告应用补丁或升级系统。作为临时缓解，可在 IE 安全设置中禁用\"对未标记为安全的 ActiveX 控件初始化并执行脚本\"并在受信任站点区域移除不可信站点。升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本可彻底消除该漏洞风险。建议卸载 SystemWizard 组件或删除相关 ActiveX 控件 CLSID 注册表键值。作为临时缓解，可在 IE 安全设置中禁用 ActiveX 控件脚本执行权限。参考 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 应用补丁或升级系统版本彻底修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93336970231857&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/555","http://www.systemsoft.com/l-2/l-3/support-systemwizard.htm","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1206.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1206","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1206.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f298f72e4ec0bc0f6b7151db8bb167727c83d2d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1206.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gjmg-cjcp-mhwg/GHSA-gjmg-cjcp-mhwg.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/555/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1206.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001007.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1010.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1002","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1177","title":"Nph-publish 目录遍历任意文件写入漏洞","description":"nph-publish 1.2 之前版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者在文件上传操作的路径名中使用 `..`（点点）目录遍历序列，可绕过路径限制以 Web 服务器权限覆盖任意文件。攻击者可通过上传恶意脚本覆盖关键文件导致远程代码执行或服务中断，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1177"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.990","remediation":"立即升级 nph-publish 至 1.2 或更高版本（下载地址：http://stein.cshl.org/~lstein/server_publish/）。如无法升级，直接删除或移除 nph-publish 脚本的执行权限（chmod -x nph-publish）。同时确保 Web 服务器以最低权限用户（非 root）运行，并将上传目标目录权限设置为非全局可写，避免攻击者利用目录遍历覆盖任意文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www-genome.wi.mit.edu/WWW/tools/CGI_scripts/server_publish/nph-publish","http://www.w3.org/Security/Faq/wwwsf4.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2055","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-1177.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1177.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-1177.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1177","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1177.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-1177.yaml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v755-q23g-3hrx/GHSA-v755-q23g-3hrx.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1177.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/nph-publish.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1002.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1002.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1001","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1175","title":"Cisco IOS Cache Engine Web Cache Control Protocol 认证漏洞","description":"tags.<value>Cisco IOS 11.2 及更早版本所配套的 Cisco Cache Engine 在实现 Web 缓存控制协议（WCCP）时未引入任何认证机制。WCCP 通过 UDP 2048 端口通信，用于协调缓存引擎与路由器之间的流量重定向。由于协议缺乏身份校验，未经过认证的远程攻击者可向目标路由器的 UDP 2048 端口伪造并发送 WCCP 报文，从而将经过该设备的 HTTP 流量重定向至攻击者可控的任意主机，进而实施中间人劫持、流量监听或钓鱼攻击。该漏洞影响运行 Cisco IOS 11.2 及更早版本且启用 WCCP 功能的 Cisco 网络设备与缓存引擎，攻击只需网络可达目标 UDP 2048 端口，无需本地权限或用户交互，利用门槛低、危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1175"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.753","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 11.3 或更高版本以启用 WCCP 身份验证功能；若暂时无法升级，请在路由器上执行 \"no ip wccp\" 命令禁用 WCCP 服务，或在防火墙层面阻断 UDP 2048 端口防止未授权流量重定向。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-054.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/wccpauth-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1577","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-1175.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1175","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1175.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2qg5-3mg4-mrr4/GHSA-2qg5-3mg4-mrr4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/C/cisco-sa-19980513-wccp-auth.nasl","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001005.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--71565265-4d4c-43b5-9801-c1bbf5c6174a.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0996","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0996.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1167","title":"Third Voice Web Annotation 跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Third Voice Web Annotation 注释工具存在跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞。远程攻击者可在网页注释中注入恶意 JavaScript 代码，当其他 Third Voice 用户浏览同一页面并加载注释时，恶意脚本将在用户浏览器中自动执行，导致攻击者可窃取用户 Cookie 及敏感数据，或伪造网页内容实施钓鱼攻击。该漏洞影响 Third Voice 注释扩展所有版本，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。用户需警惕不明来源注释，建议卸载该软件以消除风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1167"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.783","remediation":"立即卸载 Third Voice 软件（该产品已停止维护，于 2000 年左右退出市场且不再发布安全更新）。在浏览器扩展管理中移除所有 Third Voice 相关插件。替代方案：使用现代浏览器内置注释功能或基于服务端的内容注释工具（如 Hypothes.is），这些方案默认对用户输入进行转义处理并实施 CSP 策略，可有效防范 XSS 攻击。如需继续使用第三方注释系统，应启用 Content-Security-Policy HTTP 头并配置 `script-src` 限制内联脚本执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7252.php","http://www.wired.com/news/technology/0%2C1282%2C20636%2C00.html","http://www.wired.com/news/technology/0%2C1282%2C20677%2C00.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d39c6fc359564f87c4fbc1b2c3e7c679c878fdd9/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1167","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1167.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/b61a9cff022af7967458616078d0be1725a7f46a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qgpq-pjxc-x5wq/GHSA-qgpq-pjxc-x5wq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83040/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e64526992db40c94520d0244d04a3aa859684904/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0996.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0988","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0988.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1157","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 ICMP 子网掩码请求拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的 tcpip.sys 在处理 ICMP Subnet Mask Address Request 数据包时存在缺陷，当多个 IP 地址绑定到同一网络接口时，远程攻击者可通过发送特制的 ICMP 子网掩码请求报文触发该漏洞，导致目标系统服务崩溃。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP4 之前版本，需目标配置多 IP 绑定环境，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1157"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:50.523","remediation":"建议安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 (SP4) 或更高版本，SP4 已修复了 tcpip.sys 对 ICMP Subnet Mask 请求处理不当导致的拒绝服务问题。临时缓解方案：在边界防火墙上过滤入站 ICMP 类型 17 代码 0（子网掩码请求）数据包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q192/7/74.ASP","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3894"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0988.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0978","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0978.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1132","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Routing Information Field 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 在处理令牌环网络中的源路由数据时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，向目标系统发送特制的 Routing Information Field（RIF）数据包，构造跳数超过 7 的冗余路由条目，或包含重复的 Token Ring ID，即可触发内核错误，导致目标系统蓝屏崩溃。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系列操作系统，攻击成本低、无需用户交互，属于中等危害的拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1132"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.313","remediation":"根本修复方案：由于 Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019 或 2022）。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙或路由器上配置 ACL 规则，丢弃源路由选项（Source Routing）数据包，阻止含有异常 RIF 跳数（>7）或重复 Token Ring ID 的 Token Ring 源路由帧进入内部网络。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90763508011966&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=90760603030452&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q179/1/57.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/1399.php"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0978.toml"}]